<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Story - jlegal.pro</title>
    <meta name="description" content="A figure-first narrative showing how three tracks converged: building management, assault-system response, and family trust actions.">
    <meta property="og:title" content="The Story - Three Tracks, One Convergence">
    <meta property="og:description" content="A Jewish tenant was assaulted, exposed to toxic VOCs, and displaced. This page shows how three tracks converged in one timeline.">
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://jlegal.pro/og-thumbnail.png">
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://jlegal.pro/story.html">
    <meta property="og:type" content="article">
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="jlegal.pro">
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="The Story - Three Tracks, One Convergence">
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="Figure-first timeline of how three tracks converged on displacement.">
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://jlegal.pro/og-thumbnail.png">
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://jlegal.pro/story.html">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #0c0c0e;
            --bg-elevated: #131316;
            --bg-card: #18181c;
            --text: #e8e6e2;
            --text-dim: #C0BEB6;
            --line: rgba(232, 230, 226, 0.1);
            --color-red: #c4352a;
            --color-teal: #6BA3A5;
            --color-gold: #8b7355;
            --color-gold-link: #C4A97D;
            --color-red-glow: rgba(196, 53, 42, 0.3);
            --color-teal-glow: rgba(107, 163, 165, 0.3);
            --color-gold-glow: rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.3);
            --serif: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
            --sans: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            --max-w: 1080px;
            --reading-w: 760px;
            --section-gap: 88px;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            font-family: var(--sans);
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.75;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .skip-link {
            position: absolute;
            top: -120px;
            left: 20px;
            z-index: 1200;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            color: var(--text);
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 14px;
            border: 2px solid var(--color-gold-link);
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--color-gold-glow);
            font-size: 13px;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .skip-link:focus {
            top: 12px;
        }

        a {
            color: var(--color-gold-link);
            text-underline-offset: 0.2em;
        }

        a:hover {
            color: var(--text);
        }

        a:focus-visible {
            outline: 2px solid var(--color-gold-link);
            outline-offset: 3px;
        }

        .sticky-nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            background: rgba(12, 12, 14, 0.88);
            backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
            padding: 12px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            transform: translateY(-100%);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, opacity 0.3s ease;
        }

        .sticky-nav.visible {
            transform: translateY(0);
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .sticky-nav:not(.visible) {
            visibility: hidden;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .sticky-nav .nav-title {
            font-family: var(--serif);
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .sticky-nav .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 14px;
        }

        .sticky-nav .nav-link {
            font-size: 13px;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--color-gold-link);
            padding: 10px 12px;
            min-height: 44px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .container {
            width: min(var(--max-w), 100%);
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 24px;
        }

        .reading {
            width: min(var(--reading-w), 100%);
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        section {
            scroll-margin-top: 80px;
        }

        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            min-height: 100dvh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 72px 24px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-family: var(--serif);
            font-size: clamp(42px, 9vw, 76px);
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            letter-spacing: -0.01em;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out both;
        }

        .hero .meta {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            letter-spacing: 0.09em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 22px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.2s both;
        }

        .hero .line {
            width: 68px;
            height: 1px;
            background: var(--color-gold-link);
            margin: 0 auto 24px;
            animation: drawLine 0.6s ease-out 0.4s both;
        }

        .hero .hook {
            font-family: var(--serif);
            font-size: clamp(20px, 3.1vw, 30px);
            line-height: 1.55;
            max-width: 860px;
            font-style: italic;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.6s both;
        }

        .hero .hook-sub {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--text-dim);
        }

        .section {
            padding: var(--section-gap) 0;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-family: var(--serif);
            font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 40px);
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .section-subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            font-size: 15px;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 34px;
        }

        .summary-card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold-link);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .summary-card ul {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .summary-card li {
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            padding-left: 22px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .summary-card li::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 11px;
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--color-gold-link);
        }

        .path {
            margin-top: 26px;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border: 1px dashed rgba(184, 154, 114, 0.5);
            border-radius: 5px;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            font-size: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .figure {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .figure + .figure {
            margin-top: 26px;
        }

        .figure h3 {
            font-family: var(--serif);
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .figure p {
            color: var(--text-dim);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .swimlane-chart {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr;
            gap: 12px;
            align-items: start;
            margin-top: 6px;
        }

        .axis {
            grid-column: 2;
            position: relative;
            height: 28px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
        }

        .axis span {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 4px;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            font-size: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .lane-label {
            font-family: var(--serif);
            font-size: 19px;
            text-align: right;
            padding-top: 24px;
        }

        .lane-label.red { color: var(--color-red); }
        .lane-label.teal { color: var(--color-teal); }
        .lane-label.gold { color: var(--color-gold-link); }

        .lane {
            position: relative;
            min-height: 78px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
            padding-top: 18px;
        }

        .lane::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            top: 24px;
            height: 2px;
            background: rgba(232, 230, 226, 0.09);
        }

        .guide {
            position: absolute;
            top: -28px;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 1px;
            background: rgba(232, 230, 226, 0.2);
        }

        .guide.strong {
            width: 2px;
            background: rgba(232, 230, 226, 0.35);
        }

        .event {
            position: absolute;
            top: 8px;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 132px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 11px;
            line-height: 1.3;
            color: var(--text-dim);
        }

        .event .dot {
            width: 11px;
            height: 11px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto 6px;
        }

        .event.red .dot { background: var(--color-red); }
        .event.teal .dot { background: var(--color-teal); }
        .event.gold .dot { background: var(--color-gold-link); }

        .event.multi .dot {
            border-radius: 2px;
            transform: rotate(45deg);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-red), var(--color-gold-link));
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(232, 230, 226, 0.2);
        }

        .event strong {
            display: block;
            color: var(--text);
            font-size: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }

        .event.red { box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--color-red-glow); }
        .event.teal { box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--color-teal-glow); }
        .event.gold { box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--color-gold-glow); }
        .event.multi { box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--color-red-glow), 0 0 12px var(--color-gold-glow); }

        .event:hover { transform: scale(1.3); transition: transform 0.2s ease; }

        .figure-note {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
            padding-top: 14px;
        }

        .matrix-table,
        .evidence-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .matrix-table th,
        .matrix-table td,
        .evidence-table th,
        .evidence-table td {
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            padding: 11px 12px;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .matrix-table th,
        .evidence-table th {
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.07em;
            color: var(--color-gold-link);
            background: var(--bg-elevated);
        }

        .matrix-table td {
            color: var(--text-dim);
        }

        .matrix-table td:first-child {
            color: var(--text);
            white-space: nowrap;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .tracks-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .track {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-top: 3px solid;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 18px 16px 16px;
        }

        .track.red { border-top-color: var(--color-red); }
        .track.teal { border-top-color: var(--color-teal); }
        .track.gold { border-top-color: var(--color-gold-link); }

        .track h3 {
            font-family: var(--serif);
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .track ol {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .track li {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.55;
        }

        .track li::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 8px;
            width: 7px;
            height: 7px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: currentColor;
            opacity: 0.85;
        }

        .track time {
            display: block;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.07em;
            color: var(--text);
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }

        .quote-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 16px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        blockquote {
            background: var(--bg-elevated);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--color-red);
            padding: 18px 16px;
            font-family: var(--serif);
            font-size: 21px;
            line-height: 1.45;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .pullquote {
            margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);
            margin-right: calc(-50vw + 50%);
            width: 100vw;
            padding: 48px 8vw;
            border-left: 6px solid var(--color-red);
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(196,53,42,0.08) 0%, rgba(196,53,42,0.02) 100%);
        }

        .pullquote.teal {
            border-left-color: var(--color-teal);
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(74,124,126,0.08) 0%, rgba(74,124,126,0.02) 100%);
        }

        .pullquote.gold {
            border-left-color: var(--color-gold);
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(139,115,85,0.08) 0%, rgba(139,115,85,0.02) 100%);
        }

        blockquote cite {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 12px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-family: var(--sans);
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .closing {
            border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
            margin-top: var(--section-gap);
            padding-top: var(--section-gap);
        }

        .closing p {
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .architecture {
            font-family: var(--serif);
            font-size: 32px;
            color: var(--color-red);
            font-style: italic;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        footer {
            border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
            margin-top: var(--section-gap);
            padding: 46px 0 64px;
        }

        footer .footer-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        footer nav {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px 26px;
        }

        footer nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--color-gold-link);
            font-size: 14px;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            min-height: 44px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        @media (max-width: 980px) {
            .tracks-grid,
            .quote-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 860px) {
            .swimlane-chart {
                display: block;
            }

            .axis,
            .lane-label {
                display: none;
            }

            .lane {
                min-height: auto;
                padding-top: 0;
                margin-bottom: 18px;
            }

            .lane::before,
            .guide {
                display: none;
            }

            .event {
                position: static;
                transform: none;
                width: 100%;
                text-align: left;
                display: flex;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 10px;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            .event .dot {
                margin: 4px 0 0;
            }

            .event strong {
                display: inline;
                margin-right: 6px;
                font-size: 11px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 767px) {
            body {
                font-size: 17px;
            }

            .hero {
                min-height: 88vh;
                min-height: 88dvh;
            }

            .hero .hook {
                font-size: 20px;
            }

            .section {
                padding: 64px 0;
            }

            .figure {
                padding: 18px;
            }

            .track li {
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            .track-entry {
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            .matrix-table,
            .evidence-table {
                display: block;
                overflow-x: auto;
                font-size: 15px;
            }

            .matrix-table td,
            .evidence-table td {
                padding: 8px 10px;
                word-break: break-word;
            }

            table {
                white-space: normal;
            }

            blockquote {
                font-size: 18px;
            }
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1023px) {
            .tracks-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 28px; }
            .quote-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
            .container { padding: 0 32px; }
        }

        @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
            html {
                scroll-behavior: auto;
            }

            .sticky-nav {
                transition: none;
            }

            .hero h1,
            .hero .meta,
            .hero .hook {
                animation: none;
            }

            .hero .line {
                animation: none;
            }
        }

        .reading-progress { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; height: 3px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-red), var(--color-teal), var(--color-gold)); width: 0%; z-index: 1001; transition: width 0.05s linear; pointer-events: none; }

        .merge-visual { position: relative; height: 200px; margin: 60px auto; max-width: 400px; overflow: hidden; }
        .merge-line { position: absolute; bottom: 0; width: 3px; opacity: 0; height: 0; transition: height 0.8s ease-out, opacity 0.6s ease-out; }
        .merge-line.animate { height: 100%; opacity: 1; }
        .merge-line--red { left: 20%; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--color-red), var(--text)); transform: skewX(12deg); }
        .merge-line--teal { left: calc(50% - 1.5px); background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--color-teal), var(--text)); }
        .merge-line--gold { left: 80%; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--color-gold), var(--text)); transform: skewX(-12deg); }
        .merge-visual::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: calc(50% - 5px); width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--text); box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--color-red), 0 0 30px var(--color-teal), 0 0 20px var(--color-gold); }

        [data-date] { transition: opacity 0.3s ease; }
        .date-highlight { opacity: 1; background: rgba(196,53,42,0.2); border-radius: 4px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-red); padding-bottom: 2px; }
        .date-dim { opacity: 0.3; }

        @keyframes fadeInUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
        @keyframes drawLine { from { width: 0; } to { width: 80px; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="reading-progress" id="readingProgress"></div>
<a href="#main-content" class="skip-link">Skip to main content</a>

<nav class="sticky-nav" id="stickyNav" aria-label="Page navigation" aria-hidden="true">
    <span class="nav-title">The Story</span>
    <div class="nav-links">
        <a class="nav-link" href="three-surfaces.html">Three Surfaces</a>
        <a class="nav-link" href="index.html">Full Report</a>
    </div>
</nav>

<header class="hero" id="hero">
    <div>
        <h1>The Story</h1>
        <p class="meta">Justin Horn | Philadelphia | 2025-2026</p>
        <div class="line" role="presentation"></div>
        <p class="hook">A Jewish tenant was assaulted, exposed to toxic VOCs, and displaced. Three tracks converged in one window.</p>
        <p class="hook-sub">This page starts with figures, then drills down into each track.</p>
    </div>
</header>

<main id="main-content">
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="reading">
                <h2 class="section-title">What this page proves</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">One timeline | Three tracks | One outcome</p>
                <div class="summary-card">
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Track 1 - The Building:</strong> HVAC failure, toxic off-gassing, notice on video, then displacement pressure.</li>
                        <li><strong>Track 2 - The Assault/System response:</strong> violent assault, evidence suppression behavior, and official refusal points.</li>
                        <li><strong>Track 3 - The Family/Trust:</strong> financial control decisions that kept rent flowing to an unlicensed landlord.</li>
                        <li><strong>Convergence window:</strong> late February through mid-May 2026 shows repeated same-direction decisions.</li>
                        <li><strong>Outcome:</strong> by May 5 he could not safely remain in the unit; on May 6 he was transported by ambulance to the ER.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="path">Reader path: <a href="story.html">Story</a> -> <a href="three-surfaces.html">Three Surfaces</a> -> <a href="index.html#critical-findings">Critical Findings</a> -> <a href="evidence-photos.html">Evidence Photos</a> / <a href="audio-analysis.html">Audio Analysis</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <figure class="figure">
                <figcaption><h3>Figure 1 - Synchronized convergence swimlane</h3></figcaption>
                <p>Three tracks mapped to one date axis. Vertical guides mark shared hinge dates.</p>

                <div class="swimlane-chart" aria-hidden="true">
                    <div class="axis">
                        <span style="left: 2%;">Aug '25</span>
                        <span style="left: 15%;">Oct '25</span>
                        <span style="left: 31%;">Dec '25</span>
                        <span style="left: 52%;">Feb '26</span>
                        <span style="left: 66%;">Apr '26</span>
                        <span style="left: 81%;">May '26</span>
                        <span style="left: 96%;">Jun '26</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="lane-label red" aria-label="Building track (red)">Building</div>
                    <div class="lane">
                        <span class="guide" style="left: 52%;"></span>
                        <span class="guide" style="left: 69%;"></span>
                        <span class="guide strong" style="left: 81%;"></span>
                        <div class="event red" style="left: 11%;"><span class="dot"></span><div><strong>Sept 2025</strong>HVAC fails</div></div>
                        <div class="event multi" data-date="2026-02-28" style="left: 52%;"><span class="dot"></span><div><strong>Feb 28</strong>License expires</div></div>
                        <div class="event red" style="left: 66%;"><span class="dot"></span><div><strong>Apr 6</strong>FSK tape + off-gassing</div></div>
                        <div class="event multi" data-date="2026-04-15" style="left: 69%;"><span class="dot"></span><div><strong>Apr 15</strong>On camera + police called + non-renewal</div></div>
