    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="reading closing" id="convergence">
                <h2 class="section-title">The convergence in plain language</h2>
                <p>On May 6, the ambulance is the visible emergency point. But the convergence was built earlier: building decisions created and maintained the hazard path; system decisions degraded protection and evidence confidence; family-trust decisions constrained safe exit while payments continued.</p>
                <p>By May 5, he could not safely remain in Unit 806. On May 6, he was transported to the ER and placed on oxygen. In the same period, eviction pressure remained active and the trial calendar was already fixed.</p>
                <p>Tracks are the chronology. Surfaces are the institutional structure underneath those dates. They are two views of the same architecture.</p>
                <p class="architecture">This was not dysfunction. It was architecture.</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 20px;"><a href="three-surfaces.html">Continue: The Three Surfaces -></a></p>

                <p style="margin-top: 34px;"><strong>Status:</strong> displaced; unit assessed as total loss; SERVPRO remediation refusal documented; bodycam unresolved; trial June 12; vacate date June 15.</p>
                <p>On June 12, 2026, the trial date. On June 15, 2026, the eviction vacate date. Three days apart. The legal calendar and the displacement calendar converge again. A displaced witness in a hate crime is watching the countdown &mdash; trial on Thursday, eviction on Sunday &mdash; and waiting to see which institution, if any, chooses to do its job. None of them have chosen yet.</p>
                <p><em>This site exists because no institution acted, so the record had to be built directly.</em></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

